  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>Receive physical samples at the counter or delivery point, ensuring proper labelling and adherence to chain-of-custody requirements.</li><li>Check accompanying forms for completeness and accuracy before acceptance.</li><li>Enter sample details into the tracking system and assign appropriate codes or barcodes.</li><li>Ensure samples are stored or transferred according to temperature, safety, and handling protocols.</li><li>Communicate promptly with relevant departments for urgent or priority samples.</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Possess at least a Nitec in any field</li><li>Prior Customer Service experience is an advantage</li><li>Able to start work immediately or on short notice.</li></ul><p>For interested candidate, please email your resumes to denyse.tan@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Denyse Nicole Tan Shuqin (#HDT)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>CEI No: R1333503</p><p>Company EA license : 99C4599</p>",
